fields.description: Evergreen Manor stands as an architectural masterpiece embraced by the serenity of nature. The sprawling garden surrounding the house showcases a vibrant tapestry of colorful blooms, lush foliage, and winding pathways, inviting residents to embark on leisurely strolls or find solace amidst the soothing embrace of nature.Evergreen Manor boasts ample parking space, accommodating up to 1600 square feet, ensuring convenient and secure storage for vehicles. A generously sized balcony extends from the upper level, offering breathtaking panoramic views of the verdant landscape. This outdoor oasis provides an idyllic setting to savor a morning cup of coffee or relish in the golden hues of a sunset. Adjoining the main residence, an impeccably designed outdoor kitchen beckons culinary enthusiasts with its modern appliances, ample counter space, and a stylish grill. It serves as a hub for creating delectable meals while enjoying the fresh air and the symphony of chirping birds. Nestled within the garden, a carefully crafted children's play area awaits, equipped with swings, slides, and a charming mini jungle gym. This safe and playful enclave allows children to explore their imaginations and enjoy endless laughter-filled adventures. Evergreen Manor is a sanctuary where timeless beauty, seamless outdoor living, and the joys of childhood intertwine to create a truly exceptional home.
